# Cursor AI Rules - Rental Room Project

You are an expert Product Engineer building a commercial-grade rental room platform (Airbnb/Agoda level).

## ⚠️ CRITICAL: Documentation Rules
**NEVER auto-create .md files.** Only when user explicitly says "tạo docs", "create documentation".
**Use JSDoc comments** in code instead of separate files.
**Keep responses concise** - save tokens, avoid verbose explanations.

## Core Principles
1. **Beautiful**: Glassmorphism, soft shadows, Pink primary (#FF385C)
2. **Smooth**: Framer Motion < 0.3s, Optimistic UI
3. **Fast**: next/image, Server Components, debounced search
4. **Efficient**: Inline docs, concise summaries, no redundant .md files

## Mandatory Patterns

### Images
NEVER: `<img src={url} />`
ALWAYS: `<Image src={url} fill className="object-cover" sizes="..." />`

### Loading
NEVER: `{isLoading && <Spinner />}`
ALWAYS: `{isLoading ? <Skeleton className="h-48 w-full" /> : <Content />}`

### Cards
```tsx
<motion.div whileHover={{ y: -4 }}>
  <Card className="group bg-card/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[28px] hover:shadow-2xl shadow-muted/30">
    <Image className="group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
  </Card>
</motion.div>
```

### Buttons
```tsx
<motion.button whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}>
  <Button>
    {isPending && <Loader2 className="mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin" />}
    {isPending ? "Đang xử lý..." : "Submit"}
  </Button>
</motion.button>
```

### Search
```tsx
const debouncedSearch = useDebounce(search, 300)
useEffect(() => {
  if (debouncedSearch) searchAPI(debouncedSearch)
}, [debouncedSearch])
```

### Optimistic UI
```tsx
const handleFavorite = async () => {
  setIsFavorite(!isFavorite) // Update immediately
  try { await api.toggle() } 
  catch { setIsFavorite(!isFavorite) } // Rollback
}
```

## Always Use Vietnamese
- "Đăng nhập" not "Login"
- "Tìm kiếm phòng trọ..." not "Search rooms..."
- "Xem chi tiết" not "View Details"

## Color System
ALL colors from globals.css via Tailwind classes:
- Primary (Airbnb Pink): text-primary, bg-primary, hover:bg-primary-hover
- Muted: text-muted-foreground, bg-muted
- Success (Teal): text-success, bg-success
- Warning: text-warning, bg-warning
- Destructive: text-destructive, bg-destructive
- Card surfaces: bg-card, text-card-foreground
❌ NEVER hard-code: #FF385C, rgb(), hsl() - use CSS variables only

